title: Spain 50 Year Bond Yield
description: Spain 50Y was 3.51 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Spain 50 Year Bond Yield reached an all time high of 4.15 in October of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for Spain 50 Year Bond Yield.
author: Tesoro Público
